name: language_html_data_url_javascript_scheme
description: |
  The value is the JavaScript URL scheme with no script body. URL-valued sinks
  require scheme allowlisting in addition to HTML attribute encoding; escaping
  quotes does not make an active scheme safe.

  The URL parser's scheme handling is defined here:
  https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#scheme-state
format: utf8-strip
decode-as: ascii
pair:
  - with: tabbed-javascript-scheme.input
    hint: tricky
  - with: entity-javascript-scheme.input
    hint: tricky
tags:
  - "language"
  - "html"
  - "xss"
  - "xss-data"
  - "url-context"
  - "javascript-url"
  - "scheme-validation"
  - "active-content-sink"
---
javascript:
